701094f-a.title: Bronx: Franklin Avenue - 169th Street (East)
701094f-a.text:
1319 to 1327 Franklin Ave., north of the N.W. corner of East 169th
Street, showing the Randall House in which S.S. Randall Jr. lived from
1861 to 1912. The G.W. Bromley map of 1923 as revised to September 1932
shows the site to be occupied by two 5-story apartment houses.
